data.description: Move in ready 2 bed, 1 bath freshly painted attached home with spacious living room, wood stove, dining area with vaulted ceilings, with slider to side patio. Cute kitchen with breakfast bar. Bedrooms have dual closets, larger room has built-in organizer and slider to back patio. Laundry room with additional storage could double as pantry and workshop. Fully fenced yard. Side patio has a storage closet, additional shed in the back yard. Single car garage. Close to highway, schools, shopping, and recreation.
